org.apache.cassandra.db.marshal

Class DateRangeType

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.cassandra.db.marshal.AbstractType<DateRange>
      • org.apache.cassandra.db.marshal.DateRangeType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Comparator<java.nio.ByteBuffer>, org.apache.cassandra.cql3.AssignmentTestable

    public class DateRangeType
extends org.apache.cassandra.db.marshal.AbstractType<DateRange>
    Date range C* type with lower and upper bounds represented as timestamps with a millisecond precision. Backing C* type for Solr type DateRangeField. CQL input must be a valid DateRangeField string.
